     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:66271e820d7de6de5fe485ae92d1cc1360ad336138d4a5220cfda205cfa465e1ace74e1c832d9a43a71bbbca12426d20baf6433145470f9f32880ca5bf0fea5b

         SOURCE2=steghide_0.5.1-9.diff.gz
